<h1 id="4.-Perform-a-hypothesis-test-to-determine-if-there-is-a-significant-difference-in-the-mean-Flow-Duration-between-Normal-Traffic-and-Attack-classes.-State-your-null-and-alternative-hypotheses,-choose-an-appropriate-test,-perform-it,-and-interpret-the-results.">4. Perform a hypothesis test to determine if there is a significant difference in the mean Flow Duration between Normal Traffic and Attack classes. State your null and alternative hypotheses, choose an appropriate test, perform it, and interpret the results.<a class="anchor-link" href="#4.-Perform-a-hypothesis-test-to-determine-if-there-is-a-significant-difference-in-the-mean-Flow-Duration-between-Normal-Traffic-and-Attack-classes.-State-your-null-and-alternative-hypotheses,-choose-an-appropriate-test,-perform-it,-and-interpret-the-results.">¶</a></h1>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell" id="cell-id=b54076cc-603f-46b0-8618-277eba0b0ee5">
<div class="jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex="0">
